text: Frank Andreasen is a Danish darts player. ==Career== Andreasen has been playing darts professionally since 2015, in which he won the Danish darts championship, beating Per Laursen in the finale. This victory ensured him a spot in the Winmau World Masters, in which he finished in the Last 80.Fyens.dk "Bedst til dark: Frank snød dem alle" ==References== ==External links== * Profile at Darts Database Category:Danish darts players Category:Living people Category:People from Assens Municipality Category:British Darts Organisation players Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
